OL,3,CLabour lose control of more Yorkshire
OL,4,Ccouncils following local elections
OL,6,FLabour has lost control of Bradford
OL,7,Fand Calderdale Councils as Reform made
OL,8,Fgains across the region following the
OL,9,Flocal elections.
OL,11,FThe Labour Party had majorities in
OL,12,Fboth of the councils until Thursday's
OL,13,Felection, following which Reform came
OL,14,Fout on top.
OL,16,FNigel Farage's party ousted the Labour
OL,17,FParty in Calderdale, who had been in
OL,18,Fcontrol since 2019, securing a
OL,19,Fmajority on the council with 34 seats
OL,20,Fto Labour's 8.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
