CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1778429470
OL,3,CLabour lose control of more Yorkshire
OL,4,Ccouncils following local elections
OL,6,FElsewhere, Reform's rise in Bradford
OL,7,Fresulted in the council having no
OL,8,Foverall majority and the leader of the
OL,9,Fcouncil, Susan Hinchcliffe, losing her
OL,10,Fseat after a decade as leader.
OL,12,FAsked how she felt about the results,
OL,13,FMs Hinchcliffe told the Local
OL,14,FDemocracy Reporting Service: "I'll be
OL,15,Ffine, it's not about me. I'm thinking
OL,16,Fmore about the other Labour
OL,17,FCouncillors who have lost their seats
OL,18,Fwho work so hard for residents day in,
OL,19,Fday out.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1778429470
OL,3,CLabour lose control of more Yorkshire
OL,4,Ccouncils following local elections
OL,6,F"What we heard on the doorstep was
OL,7,Fpeople wanted to send a message to
OL,8,FKeir Starmer. That message will have
OL,9,Fbeen heard loud and clear.
OL,11,F"But this is politics - it is a
OL,12,Fdemocracy, and we always respect the
OL,13,Fwill of the people. We have to accept
OL,14,Fthe result."
OL,16,FReform took the most seats in the
OL,17,FBradford district with 29. The
OL,18,FConservatives took 18 and Labour
OL,19,Fwalked away with 17 seats, compared to
OL,20,Fthe 46 they previously held.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1778429470
OL,3,CLabour lose control of more Yorkshire
OL,4,Ccouncils following local elections
OL,6,FMP for Bradford East, Imran Hussain,
OL,7,Fsaid: "This is a disastrous result,
OL,8,Fthere is no other way of looking at
OL,9,Fthis."
OL,11,FHe said the main problems were
OL,12,F"factionalism at the top" of the
OL,13,Fnational party.
OL,15,F"Bad choices have brought us to this
OL,16,Fplace. It is absolutely clear that
OL,17,FKeir Starmer won't be leading us into
OL,18,Fany further elections", he added.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
