FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1778429470
OL,3,CLabour lose control of more Yorkshire
OL,4,Ccouncils following local elections
OL,6,FReform Councillor Sally Birch, who won
OL,7,Fone of the Windhill and Wrose seats,
OL,8,Fsaid: "People we spoke to said they
OL,9,Fwanted something different. We believe
OL,10,Fwe can offer something different.
OL,11,FWe've been out talking to people and
OL,12,Flistening."
OL,14,FIn Kirklees, Labour failed to secure a
OL,15,Fsingle seat on the council and there
OL,16,Fis still no overall control.
OL,18,FReform became the largest party on the
OL,19,Fcouncil, winning 29 seats, after
OL,20,Fpreviously having no representation.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
