PN,36106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1778429470
OL,3,CLabour lose control of more Yorkshire
OL,4,Ccouncils following local elections
OL,6,FThe party secured a clean sweep across
OL,7,Fseven specific wards, winning all
OL,8,Fthree available seats and ousting two
OL,9,Fparty leaders.
OL,11,FIndependent candidates took 14 seats,
OL,12,Fthe Green Party took 12, Conservatives
OL,13,Ftook 9 and the Liberal Democrats
OL,14,Fsecured 5.
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
